data.description: Step into luxury and entertainment at its finest with this stunning home nestled in an upscale community with top rated schools.The ultimate dream home that offers wide open spaces;perfect for all entertaining needs.No doubt you'll instantly fall in love with the spacious,inviting atmosphere.The large kitchen,designed with the family chef in mind,a culinary haven for creating tasteful goodness while guests mingle in the cozy living area.Prepare for epic movie nights in the media room, or game night with the family!With its versatility and functionality, the 5th bedroom serves as a perfect office space for those who work remotely.Easy commute and access for home,work and play!In addition to its numerous features, this home boasts a large backyard oasis,perfect for relaxing through all Texas seasons.Don't miss the opportunity to own this captivating home that seamlessly combines luxury, functionality,and entertainment.Come experience true modern living-schedule your showing today!
